Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:04.35,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,By the decision of Ying Zheng, the king that wished to unite all of China,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:04.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N天下統一の道を行く王 嬴政(えいせい)のもと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.10,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the State of Qin began its invasion of the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:07.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国(しんこく)は 魏国(ぎこく)へと侵攻した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:11.48,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The enemy blocking their way is the legendary Great General, Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ちはだかる敵は\N伝説の大将軍 廉頗(れんぱ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:17.78,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Young generals take on this relentless battlefield in hopes of rendering great military achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若き将たちは 大いなる武功を狙い\Nこの苛烈な戦場に挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:26.95,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we have the Yuehua Unit, the Yufeng Unit, and the Feixin Unit attack in a group
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:25.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）\N明日 楽華(がくか)隊 玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊 飛信(ひしん)隊の―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３隊で打って出て\N輪虎(りんこ)を討ち取ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.37,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,and take down Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll tell it to you. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）じゃ 作戦を言おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:36.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,First, the Yuehua Unit will target Lun Hu's headquarters on our own. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは\N楽華隊が単独で輪虎の本陣を目指す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.30,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:39.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:42.81,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.09,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,For the first stage of the plan... {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）作戦の第１段階
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:54.69,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,the Yuehua Unit will not target Lun Hu. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:54.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊は輪虎を狙わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:00.78,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.25\c&H000000&\pos(638,101.667)}United Front of Three Units
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:08.54,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,They divided a mere 800 soldiers into five groups? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:08.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僅か800の兵を 更に５つに割った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:15.55,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Just what is this force supposed to do against my headquarters of 5,000? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）\N5,000からなる この本陣に対し―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:15.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに何の意味がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:18.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！ 入るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.42,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Okay, we're heading in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 普通に入ってくるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.43,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,And they're just going to come in normally? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:27.81,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,That's not clever, it's just eccentric. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:27.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ\N奇策じゃなくて 奇行でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.46,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,You're just going to die pointlessly. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:31.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただムダに死ぬだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:34.84,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Ao! The young lord...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:37.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫(かくきょう)）蒙驁(もうごう)さま 若君が…\N楽華隊が単独で敵本陣に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.35,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Yuehua Unit is attacking the enemy headquarters alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）蒙恬… 一体 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.54,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Meng Tian...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.82,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Just what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）すぐに呼び戻せ！\N（伝令）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We must call them back immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:45.33,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.00,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）いや 待て\N（伝令）はぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:48.83,Kingdom-Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:53.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,Father, about Meng Tian, {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:53.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙武(もうぶ)）親父(おやじ)どの 蒙恬のことだが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:57.93,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,is he still halted as a 300-Man General? {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙武）\Nまだ三百人将にとどめているのか？\N過保護は成長を妨げるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,Being overprotective will hinder his growth. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:03.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）\Nお前は ほったらかしすぎなのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:03.39,Kingdom-Flashback,Ao,0,0,0,,You're too negligent. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:07.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,You should have a bit more faith in him. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:08.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し あいつを信用してやれ\N（蒙驁）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙武）なよついたガキだが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,He may be a bit of a gentle child,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは そこらの千人将より\Nはるかに ものが見えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:14.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,but he's far more perceptive than most of the Thousand-Man Generals around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:19.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは親父どのが\Nいちばん分かってるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:19.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,You know that better than anyone, Father. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.99,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,Trust in Meng Tian. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙武）蒙恬を信じてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:27.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Wu,0,0,0,,If he dies, that means that's all of a man he was. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:27.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだら 死んだで\Nそれまでの男だったということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:30.50,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Meng Tian...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）蒙恬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.92,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Grandpa, check it out! A crab! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\Nじいちゃん 見て！ ほら カニ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）\N土門(どもん)将軍に伝令じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.46,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Send this message to General Tu Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:44.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）\N〝楽華隊は独立遊軍〞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:47.84,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The Yuehua Unit is an independent unit. Allow them act on their own discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〝このまま自由に\Nやらせるように〞と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）\Nハッ… し… しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,B-But sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）行け！\N（伝令）は… ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.97,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I know, Meng Tian. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）分かっておるよ 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:03.03,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I know you're the most talented of these three generations of the Meng family... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:02.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が 我ら蒙家三代で\N最も才能があることは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.64,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,But... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.04,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I absolutely cannot allow you to die pointlessly! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）\N無駄死にだけはするでないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:16.25,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy has invaded us unexpectedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）敵は\N思いのほか侵入してきています！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭）どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）守備の継ぎ目を\N狙ってくるからでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.63,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,They're probably targeting the joining points of the defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:26.30,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,If that's their plan, it sure is a shallow one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:26.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが策だっていうんなら\Nやっぱり浅はかだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.57,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Cause of course, in those areas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）\Nそういう所には ちゃんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:37.48,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I've made sure to place my own veteran soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）百戦錬磨の僕の兵が\N配置してあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.49,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）蒙恬さま！\N（蒙恬）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.20,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:48.28,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,There you are, Lun Hu soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出たな 輪虎兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水(そすい)）ここは\N歩兵に任せて問題なさそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:56.01,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like there will be any problem leaving this area to the foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬隊は\Nいつでも出られます 信(しん)どの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.96,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,The mounted unit can leave any time, Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）信どの…\N（信）ンンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.07,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Lord Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:03.96,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,You're not gonna go after Lun Hu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）輪虎を狙わないって？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.72,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Meng Tian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？ 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:13.22,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, the Yuehua Unit will target...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日 楽華隊が狙うのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.73,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Lun Hu's soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎兵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,The Lun Hu soldiers? You're saying you're going after his men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎兵？\N兵隊を狙うって言ってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）そうだ\N（信）“そうだ”って お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.56,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.11,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Correct?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.89,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,It's true that Lun Hu is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに輪虎はバケモノだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:34.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,But of course, he cannot break through a few hundred or a few thousand enemies on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが もちろん ヤツ１人で―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:34.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数百 数千の敵を\N突破できるわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:41.25,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,We also must consider his soldiers that he always takes into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\N輪虎の後ろには いつも必ず―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:41.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共に戦場をくぐり抜けてきた\N輪虎兵の存在がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.63,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,It is because of those soldiers he leads that Lun Hu has his great ability to penetrate enemy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:45.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その兵たちを率いてこその\N輪虎の突破力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:52.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,When Lun Hu fled his country, he took 700 elite soldiers with him to the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎は 亡命するときに―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えりすぐった700人の兵を\N魏国に連れてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:58.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが この戦で輪虎の周りに控え\N突撃の時を待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:58.64,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,In this battle, they wait around Lun Hu and only attack when the time to charge occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:04.15,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,The Yuehua Unit will target and inter those 700 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:04.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）楽華隊は\Nその700の兵たちを狙い撃ちし 葬る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:10.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Because then, it will no longer be realistically possible for Lun Hu to attack the Meng Ao headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば 現実的に―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎が蒙驁本陣を討つことは\N不可能になるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:17.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,However, this is more of a preparatory move than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）まあ でも これは―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,布石の意味のほうが\N大きいんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:18.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）布石？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.31,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Preparatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁(おうほん)）そう簡単な話ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.08,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:25.60,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,We, the Yufeng Unit fought with him on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）\N初日に 玉鳳隊は ヤツらと戦ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,個の力 集の力\Nどちらもヤツらのほうが上だった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:30.09,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,And both their strength as individuals and in groups was greater than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.71,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,Lun Hu and his soldiers are\N unstoppable once they start running.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走りだしたら\N止められぬ輪虎と その兵を―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共に出向いて討つのが\Nねらいだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.35,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,Say we're going to attack them together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.56,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,bearing that in mind, the ones to suffer the most damage from challenging them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを差し引いても\Nヤツらに挑んで 被害を受けるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.82,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,would be the Yuehua Unit, Meng Tian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊のほうだぞ 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.57,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Why don't you call for a sortie, Lord Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）\Nなぜ出撃しないのですか？ 信どの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:58.18,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Was your plan not to fight together with the Yuehua Unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:57.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊と共に戦うという\N話ではなかったのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.59,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,At this rate, the Yuehua Unit will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままでは 楽華隊は…\N（信）合図があるまで動くな！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.83,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't move until I give the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:07.34,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This is part of Meng Tian's strategy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:07.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これも蒙恬の作戦なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:12.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）賁さま\Nやはり楽華隊は苦戦しております
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:12.55,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Lord Ben, it seems the Yuehua Unit truly is fighting a difficult battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:17.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この作戦は間違いだったのでは？\N（王賁）いや そうは思わぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.38,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,I believe this strategy could have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.35,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:23.53,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,In order to take down a major player like Lun Hu, some framework for an attack is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎のような大物を討つには\N攻めの組み立てが必要になる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽）攻めの組み立て？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.86,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Framework for attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:32.86,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,When attacking Lun Hu, you can be sure that the mighty Lun Hu soldiers will be a major barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）輪虎を襲うとき―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず屈強な輪虎兵が\N大きな障壁となって立ちはだかる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:37.22,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,What Meng Tian is doing is trying to remove them beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）それを蒙恬は\N先に取り除こうとしているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.18,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Of course, that will be no easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 容易なことではない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:48.38,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,But he volunteered for this bloody first job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）ヤツは自ら―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:48.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いちばん血を流す このつぶれ役を\N買って出たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:53.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）本当に 今回は\N腹を決めているようだな 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.59,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,It looks like you've really resolved yourself this time, Meng Tian. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.11,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,The Yuehua Unit is very capricious. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:07:00.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気分屋色の強い楽華隊だ\Nお前が前面でやる気を見せれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.68,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,If you show outright enthusiasm... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,the Yuehua Unit will be greatly excited {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:05.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）楽華隊は大いに盛り上がり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.87,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,and display far greater power than usual. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふだん以上の力を発揮する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.56,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,What's wrong, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？ みんな\Nもう へばったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:12.90,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Tired already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.36,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Like hell we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.04,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,My soldiers are... being beaten? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の兵が やられてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.09,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ちょ… ちょっと待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.03,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,I don't get it, Meng Tian...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:33.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでだ？ 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:38.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで自分が踏み台に…\N犠牲になるようなマネするんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Why would you sacrifice yourself for the rest of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.47,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,and make yourself a stepping stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:43.15,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,You idiot. I don't intend to be some kind of self-sacrificing martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）バカ！\N自己犠牲の聖者のつもりはないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ この重要な役回りは―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.09,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,It's just that it's highly unlikely
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の玉鳳隊も 飛信隊も\Nこなせっこない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,that this crucial job could be accomplished by the current Yufeng or Feixin Units.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:53.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,It can only be done by the Yuehua Unit, so that's what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）やれるのは楽華隊だけ\Nだから やる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ては―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:58.74,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,This is all for the sake of defeating Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を討つために
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,By us three units!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち３隊でな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.29,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Okay, now's a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし ころ合いだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.56,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:19.15,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,So Wang Ben, Xin, I'm counting on you to take care of the rest! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）だから\N王賁 信… その先は任せたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.93,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,There's the signal, Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合図だ！ 信どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンッ！ 行くぞ！ 飛信隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's go, Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.40,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,We're heading out, Yufeng Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出るぞ 玉鳳隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:35.37,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Will the foot soldiers be all right back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣(きょうかい)）\N残していく歩兵は大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:39.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趣旨は什長(じゅうちょう)にまで伝達してある\Nそれよりも 問題は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.15,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I've informed the Shen Chiefs of our intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.53,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,The bigger question now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:45.48,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,is whether or not we can reach Lun Hu before the Yuehua Unit falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊が倒れる前に―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々が輪虎のもとへ\Nたどりつけるかどうかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N蒙恬さま！ かなり やられました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.55,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We've had some considerable losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:59.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,If we lose any more manpower, we may be completely routed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上 兵力を失うと\N一気に 総崩れになります！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.26,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:05.77,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,But the Lun Hu soldiers have been diminished just as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも その分\N輪虎兵も かなり減ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.94,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Have all of my soldiers temporarily withdraw and gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:09.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各所の僕の兵を\N一度 下げて 集結させて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭）なっ… 将軍の兵をですか？\N（輪虎）そう 急いで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.66,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Your soldiers, General!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.27,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Yes, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.37,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Send in a fresh supply of Wei soldiers to fill in the gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）\N下げた穴には 魏国軍の新手を投入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りの包囲も固めて\N１人も逃がさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.65,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,And be sure to tighten the encirclement, do not let a single person though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.29,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Man, they got me. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まいったな\N最初から僕の兵を狙ってくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.08,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I never thought they'd be going for my soldiers to start with. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:33.14,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,They're my precious arms and legs, but they're limited in their numbers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数に限りのある\N僕の貴重な手足だというのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）オリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't mind the small fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雑魚にかまうな！\N適当にあしらって すっ飛ばせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.18,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Just do what you have to to get them out of your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.01,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:52.14,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,The enemy is visibly slow in reacting to us! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:51.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）我々に対して\N敵の対応が目に見えて遅れている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:54.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隙間だ！ 隙間を駆け抜けるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We're gonna run through that opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.48,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,We can do it! We might make it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いける！ いけるかもしれない！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:03.45,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,At this rate, we can make up for starting late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:03.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この調子なら\N出遅れた分を取り戻せる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ああ 分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I told'ja, didn' I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 言ったろう\N全部 あいつの作戦どおりだって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.75,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This is all going according to that guy's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.75,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs50\be0.5\pos(1006,309.267)}Lun Hu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.79,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,"We will make it in time because we started late", sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“出遅れたから間に合う”ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ\N今回 楽華隊が突然 前に出たとき
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:21.99,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:25.16,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Earlier, when the Yuehua Unit suddenly came out early,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵は\Nほかの部隊の連動を警戒したはず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.51,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,the enemy was most likely on the lookout for other units working with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 動いたのは楽華隊のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.60,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,But the only ones that acted were the Yuehua Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.71,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,They acted alone and invaded the enemy headquarters without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:34.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）ヤツらは\N単独で躊躇(ちゅうちょ)なく敵本陣に突入し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.01,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,And so the enemy's attention became focused on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の注意は ヤツらに向いた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.42,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,The later we left,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが出るのが\N遅ければ遅いほど―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の注意は 中で暴れる楽華隊に\N集中するというわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:44.25,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,the more the enemy's attention would be concentrated on the Yuehua Unit which was among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.58,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Without those enemies as an obstacle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬隊に敵の障害さえなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:52.76,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,our mounted units should be able to reach the exposed Lun Hu headquarters in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前方に出てきている輪虎本陣までは\Nあっという間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.70,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,It's the headquarters! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）本陣だ！ いくぞ！\N（鬨の声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（じい）\N蒙恬さま！ 飛信隊 玉鳳隊が―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.84,Kingdom-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.94,Kingdom-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit and Yufeng Unit are approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,近づきつつあります\N（蒙恬）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:03.51,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:08.51,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be leaving one last meager present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:08.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ 最後にひとつ\Nささやかな贈り物をしとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.62,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Left and right units! Retreat immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左右の隊！ 一気に後退しろ！\Nここも ゆっくり下がるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.14,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,We're going to slowly retreat as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）オーッ！\N（魏兵）逃げるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.52,Kingdom-Main,Wei,0,0,0,,They're running!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.67,Kingdom-Main,Wei,0,0,0,,After them! Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）追え 追え！ 逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.82,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,There's a path opening in front of us! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前に道ができた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.90,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,L-Lord Ben, this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽）ほ… 賁さま これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.42,Kingdom-Thought,Pan,0,0,0,,It-It can't be...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽）バ… バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:36.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これも蒙恬の仕業なのか？\N信じられぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.66,Kingdom-Thought,Pan,0,0,0,,This is Meng Tian's work as well? Unbelievable.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:41.09,Kingdom-Thought,Pan,0,0,0,,We managed to get this close to one of Lian Po's close aides?  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗の側近相手に\Nこれほどの戦いをやってのけるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:47.84,Kingdom-Thought,Pan,0,0,0,,And what's more, these thee units that were so hostile before are suddenly acting together as allies. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:45.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも 反目し合っていた\Nこの３隊のにわか連合軍を―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつに まとめて…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:52.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いち早く千人将になった才能は\Nダテではない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:52.80,Kingdom-Thought,Pan,0,0,0,,His sudden transition to a Thousand-Man General was not just for show. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:59.41,Kingdom-Thought,Pan,0,0,0,,No, Meng Tian's ability may already be beyond that of a Thousand-Man General!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 蒙恬の力は―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:59.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや 千人将の域すら\N超えているかもしれぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:05.19,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-Another unit is coming from the left! It looks to be about 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）\Nひ… 左より別の隊が迫ってます！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,およそ300！\N（圭）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:08.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,O-One is coming from the right as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:10.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）み… 右からも来ます！\N（圭）バカな！ いつの間に…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Impossible! When did they have the chance...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:14.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They've already made it very close, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）既に\Nそこまで入ってきてます 将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:21.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Look! It's the headquarters' flags!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣の旗だ！\N輪虎は もう目の前だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu is right in front of us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.97,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,Lun Hu...! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.14,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,Lun Hu...! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備(かくび)兵）輪虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.38,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,Revenge for Lord Guo Bei! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,郭備さまの敵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.60,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Incoming, straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正面 来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.73,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… マズイ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.40,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,They caught us! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）捕まった！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.07,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備兵）ジャマだ！ どけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.46,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?! These guys are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）何だ？ こいつら 強(つえ)え！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:56.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,白ずくめの兵… こいつら まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.45,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Soldiers clad in white...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:59.22,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Could these ones be... Lun Hu's soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）輪虎兵か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）皆殺しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンッ！\Nここで輪虎兵が出てくるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.46,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Lun Hu soldiers are appearing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.50,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Weren't they fighting Meng Tian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こやつらは 蒙恬が\Nたたいたのではなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）輪虎の周りを固めていた\N最後の兵だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.47,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,These are Lun Hu's final soldiers that form a shield around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:17.98,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,He's unstintingly sent them to attack?! What a bold move...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽）出し惜しみなく\N繰り出してくるとは 大胆な…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つくづく攻め主体の姿勢のようだ\Nだが ここさえ抜ければ―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.94,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,They have the posture of a core attack force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:26.23,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,But if we can just make it past them, there will be no major forces left to protect Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を守る猛者たちは もういない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャマだっつってんだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.37,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,you're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay! Just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃ！ もう少しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,C-Captain, behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）た… 隊長！ 後ろが…\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.66,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The rest aren't keeping up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろが全くついてきていません！\N（信）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしている 信どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.59,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Lord Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.80,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Keep going, push your way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま突き進まれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.80,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,This is Lun Hu's final act of vain resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）\Nこれは輪虎の最後の悪あがきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.80,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,You can break through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どのなら そのまま突破できる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）アアッ！\N（信）あっ 楚水！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:57.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Chu Shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.81,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Go, Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！ 信どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:08.82,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Don't mind us, just take Lun Hu's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らにかまわず\N輪虎の首を取ってくだされ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.31,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Chu Shui... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楚水…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.12,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:15.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）殺せ！\N（楚水）ウウッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.20,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）早く行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Chu Shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楚水！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.21,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）私が戻ろう\N（信）羌瘣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この先\Nまだ あの男は飛信隊に必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.80,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit... is going to need that man in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.34,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:36.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm... going to take down Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 輪虎を討つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.50,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,The worst blow today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:47.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）今回の最大の痛手は 僕の\N私兵の大半を失ってしまったことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.92,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,will be me losing the majority of my soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:54.49,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to come up with something when going into the major stages of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:54.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 本番に向けて\N何か考えないといけなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.99,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,But that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）だけど それだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:05.83,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,There won't be anything else major.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのほかのことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に大したことではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.94,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Because being drawn on by enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）敵に迫られたところで…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.82,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,will not lead to my defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が討たれることはないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.14,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Chu Shui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無事か？ 楚水\N（楚水）きょ… 羌瘣どの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.70,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,L-Lord Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:37.14,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Why did you come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ戻ったのだ？\N（羌瘣）少し下がりながら戦うぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.36,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Let's fight while drawing back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.76,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Are you going to head back towards Lord Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どののもとへ向かうのでは？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:47.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや ここの輪虎兵を信の所へ\N連れていくのは得策じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:47.21,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,No. It wouldn't be a good plan to bring the Lun Hu soldiers to where Xin is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.86,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Let's leave Lun Hu's head... to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎の首は あいつらに任せよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:16:00.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）おや？ 君は前に…\N確か 飛信隊の…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:59.97,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Oh? You're that one from before. From the Feixin Unit I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.27,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,We meet again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また会ってしまったね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.25,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away this time, Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は逃がさねえぞ 輪虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:16.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）ハハハッ… 逆だよ\N今度は逃げてあげないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.56,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,You've got it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.87,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} won't be letting {\i1}you{\i0} run this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）…んだと？ てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.65,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What was that, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちの槍使(やりつか)い君も含めて―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.37,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,And including that spear user over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:26.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たちは 相手の力量を\Nきちんと推し量れていない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:26.62,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,you guys don't seem to have a firm grasp of your opponent's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.35,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Did you think that between the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:32.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人がかりでなら この僕を\Nどうこうできるとでも思ったのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.00,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,you might be able to somehow defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざけんな てめえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit your bullshit, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ… こんなもんで！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.89,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You think this'll work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人同時でもいいんだけど\N少々 効率よくやらせてもらうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:52.49,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have a problem with both of them at once, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.85,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,but I think I'll do this the more efficient way. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.50,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I'll leave that more manageable one for later. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くみしやすそうな君は後回し
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.78,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I do believe the one I should be attacking first is... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 先に たたいておくべきは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.38,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Lord Wang Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）王賁さま！\N（兵士）ウオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）ジャマ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.51,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハアッ！\N（輪虎）よっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.55,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Woah there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:25.93,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,You're pretty full of spirit, but I think you're a bit dull because of your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気迫は乗ってるが\Nケガのせいで キレはイマイチかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.35,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,This bastard... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.44,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Oh, that was fast. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ 速いな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.99,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Xin of the Feixin Unit, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:40.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）飛信隊の信…\Nそこまで来たなら しかたない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:40.71,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,if you've come that far, then I suppose I have no choice. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）狙っている…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.55,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,He's changing targets? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では 君から
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.20,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I'll start with you. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.24,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Stop, Xin! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれ！ し…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オリャー！\N（はじけ飛ぶ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:06.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The one that doesn't know his opponent's strength is you, Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:06.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）力量を読めてねえのは\Nお前のほうだ 輪虎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が いちばん強えのか\Nきっちり教えてやるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:13.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll pound just who it is that's the strongest into that thick skull of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）ええい\N輪虎の本陣は どうなってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's happening at Lun Hu's headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:23.53,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Damn. I can't see a thing in all the dust that's kicking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄公）\Nダメだ　乱戦の砂煙で見えぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.09,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It seems the Yuehua Unit has retreated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充(りじゅう)）楽華隊は下がったようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代わりに入っていったのは\N玉鳳隊と飛信隊か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:29.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,but in their place, both the Yufeng and Feixin Units have entered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're probably coordinating with the Yuehua Unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）楽華隊との連携だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\Nまさか３隊も身勝手に動くとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But I can't believe three units would act on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:42.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黄公）いかに独立遊軍とはいえ\N成果なくば この責任は重大だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Even if they are independent units,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:42.47,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,if they don't produce results, they will bear a hefty responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:46.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）フォフォフォ…\Nそれは当然のことじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.14,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし それは本人たちが いちばん\N分かっていることじゃろうて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:52.14,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,But those boys are the ones that know that best... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.62,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Wang Ben... Xin... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王賁… 信…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実戦向き…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.50,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Suited for combat...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:10.41,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,The sort of human that can display greater power depending on his opponent's strength, eh? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:10.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の強さによって\Nより力を発揮しだす人間か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:15.77,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Well, everyone's like that, more or less. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:15.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 誰でも 多かれ少なかれ\Nそういうものではあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この子の落差は すさまじく激しい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:18.52,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,But the difference with this boy is incredible.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして… この一撃の異常な重さ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.92,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,And this abnormal weight of individual attacks...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっとと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.60,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Woah, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえ 王賁！\Nジャマすんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.81,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, Wang Ben, don't interfere in my fight!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.90,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,You're the one interfering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャマは貴様だ\Nこいつは俺の獲物だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.56,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,He is my prey!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Fuck off, you bastard!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ざけんな てめえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）輪虎さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:56.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I-Is that man even human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）に… 人間か？ あの男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:20:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンッ… ヘヘッ… さすがに強えな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I knew you were strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:05.72,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Looks like it's true that you actually landed a blow on General Wang Qi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王騎(おうき)将軍に\Nひと太刀浴びせたってのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソじゃなさそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）その辺のことは\N茶化(ちゃか)してほしくないな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.95,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I'd prefer if you didn't make fun of things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:17.69,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose you wouldn't have any idea what opposing General Wang Qi is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎将軍を相手にすることが\Nどんなことか 分かるはずもないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）フッ… ナメんな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.88,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…んなことは\N俺たちだって分かってらぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.63,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I sure as hell know what that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくが\Nそいつは王騎将軍の一族だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But just to let you know, that guy is part of Wang Qi's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.10,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Wang Qi's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:30.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎の… では 君は？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.20,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,So, then what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:31.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺か？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:38.96,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Me? I'm the man that inherited General Wang Qi's lance and his will from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:38.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 王騎将軍から\N矛と その遺志を受け継いだ男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:43.46,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And... I'm the man that will surpass those generals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:43.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）そして\Nその将軍たちをも超える―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:48.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,and become the strongest Great General in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:48.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歴代最強の大将軍になる男だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.93,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Wang Qi's lance and will, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎の矛と遺志か…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし “歴代最強の大将軍”とは\N大きく出たねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:02.86,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,But history's strongest Great General? That's quite a claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:07.95,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That means you're also going to surpass my lord, General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:07.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ 我が主(あるじ) 廉頗将軍も\N超えるってことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前(めえ)だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yer damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:13.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,After I slay you, I'm gonna kill Lian Po while I'm at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:14.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえを討ったあと ついでに\N廉頗も ぶっ殺してやらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.52,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I do hope you don't get too full of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）\Nあんまり調子に乗らないでほしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:33.55,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Because both your lives are going to end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:33.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たちの人生は\N今日 ここで終わるんだから
